# ---- Project data & generated outputs ----
# The pipeline writes all rules, examples, answers, consistency results,
# figures, and fine-tuning checkpoints under data/ and results/. These are
# generated artifacts (see README) and are not bundled in the repository;
# large bundles are distributed via GitHub Releases.
